Day 18 - Manga 422*
Looks like something that my autistic cousin could do.
1/10.
Also, let's take a look at this rare specimen of a still alive homo erectus. As we can see, he not only makes the FUNNi NumBEr joke but also tries to get away from the brainwashed crop by becoming even more stupid. Truly a horrendous world we live in if such creature does exist. Let's all pray for his well being since he might not be able to provide that for himself.
